rong>&nbsp;with the link to your best board(s)</strong>.<br>\n<br>\nIf you haven't made any boards yet, don't wait any longer! It's simple and fun.&nbsp;Just go to <a href=\"http://learni.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=e682d21f40f033c5e91fc1903&id=87cae8ba94&e=77acee5fb9\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #26ABE2;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">your dashboard</a>&nbsp;and click 'Create a Board' to get started. We'll show you the ropes with a quick onboarding before you begin your first board.</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Want more information? <a href=\"http://learni.us5.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=e682d21f40f033c5e91fc1903&id=1d39c8c1fa&e=77acee5fb9\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #26ABE2;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">Click Here</a>&nbsp;to learn more about our content selection process or send your questions to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:submissions@learnist.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #26ABE2;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">submissions@learnist.com</a>.</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\nLearnist Team\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </tbody></table>\n\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table></td>\n                                                    </tr>\n                                                </table>\n                                            </td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                    </table>\n                                    <!-- // END BODY -->\n                                </td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table